{
  "stem": "4247.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our task was to load and offload ammunition and other items into the wagons, and also to, to dismantle-- render harmless the time bombs, which have, by that time, been dropped by the Americans and the English.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't explode.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the Americans and English, to a lesser degree, started to come up from Italy and started to bomb Hungary.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So that was a source of tremendous joy for us, right, because we realized that this is our final salvation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Although the bombs didn't seek out Jewish or non-Jewish targets, and--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--it could have killed us just as easily as the, the time bombs-- which did not function, explode-- have killed some of our, our people there, right?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I haven't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have-- personally, I have not been involved in, in handling those time bombs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But those who have been have not-- have been given five minutes training, I can assure you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they have been not really skilled in, in, in dealing with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by that time, Hungary-- no, by that time, the provincial Jews, including Ujpest-- which was the last one on the 2nd of July-- have all been deported.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In Hungary, with the return of, of the detached areas, it was about 800,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By that time, with the exception of approximately 200,000 Budapest Jews, they have all been deported.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have been all in Auschwitz or other destination.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was the situation in, in, in August, 1944.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By that time, the Hungarian government started to see very clearly-- so much more than-- knew much more than we did-- that the war is lost by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were starting to seek a, a way out.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
